&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="text-align: justify;"&gt;The room for Users Groups is one of FISL most important activities. Many activities before, during and after the event are planned having the Users Groups &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="text-align: justify;"&gt;in mind&lt;/span&gt;. The lion's share of the main hall is reserved for Users Groups (see the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="/fisl14/planta-do-evento.pdf" title="Planta fisl14 PDF" target="_blank" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;map&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href="/fisl14/imagens/planta-gus-context2.pdf" title="Planta GUs PDF" target="_blank" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;UGs map&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="text-align: justify;"&gt;). &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Groups who benefit from this room have a unique opportunity to showcase their initiatives, share with the public and press besides interaction with other Groups and sponsors.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Join us, &lt;a href="http://gus.softwarelivre.org/" title="Inscrições GUs" target="_self"&gt;register your Group&lt;/a&gt;! Oh, and if your registered your Group but are not listed above, check the requirements to complete your registration (we'll need your logo, website/list, and the name of af least four Group people that will attend the event. ;) )&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2013 19:05:34 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl14/blog/registrations-for-users-groups-were-postponed</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl14/blog/registrations-for-users-groups-were-postponed</guid></item><item><title>Prorrogamos las inscripciones de Grupos de Usuarios</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/articles/0126/7864/gus-conf.jpg" alt=""&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Aún hay tiempo como para intentar tener un lugar en la Zona Expo del FISL para tu grupo de usuarios. Las inscripciones fueron prorrogadas hasta el 23 de junio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;De los 24 grupos inscriptos, 10 completaron todos los requisitos y ya están confirmados:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://mulheresnatecnologia.org/" title="Site /MNT"&gt;/MNT - Mulheres na Tecnologia&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://flisoldf.blog.br/" target="_blank"&gt;FLISOL DF&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
